Achievements.Name: We Came, We Saw...
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on 'Casual' or 'Experienced' difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Are You A God?
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on 'Professional' difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Slam Dunk!
Achievements.Description: Slam dunk a ghost into a trap.

Achievements.Name: Slime Dunk!
Achievements.Description: Trap a ghost using the Slime Tether.

Achievements.Name: Stasis Dunk!
Achievements.Description: Trap a ghost using the Stasis Stream.

Achievements.Name: I Ain't 'Fraid of No Ghost!
Achievements.Description: Trap a ghost.

Achievements.Name: Aim for the Flat Top!
Achievements.Description: Eliminate a creature.

Achievements.Name: Heat 'Em Up
Achievements.Description: Purchase all upgrades for the Proton Gun.

Achievements.Name: Mother Pus Bucket!
Achievements.Description: Purchase all upgrades for the Slime Gun.

Achievements.Name: We be fast! They be slow!
Achievements.Description: Purchase all upgrades for the Dark Matter Generator.

Achievements.Name: I Don't Want My Face Burned Off
Achievements.Description: Purchase all upgrades for the Meson Collider.

Achievements.Name: We Have the Tools!
Achievements.Description: Purchase all available equipment upgrades.

Achievements.Name: The Destructor
Achievements.Description: Complete the game with more than $3,000,000 in property damage.

Achievements.Name: Nice Shootin', Tex!
Achievements.Description: Complete the game with less than $100,000 in property damage.

Achievements.Name: ...And You Want to Keep It?
Achievements.Description: Collect a Cursed Artifact.

Achievements.Name: Spores, Molds, and Fungus
Achievements.Description: Collect all Cursed Artifacts.

Achievements.Name: I'm Picking Up A Signal...
Achievements.Description: Obtain a 100% PKE scan on a paranormal creature.

Achievements.Name: Back Off Man. I'm a Scientist
Achievements.Description: Obtain 100% PKE scans for every paranormal creature.

Achievements.Name: I'm a Ghostbuster, Not a Doctor!
Achievements.Description: Revive your teammates 20 times.

Achievements.Name: I Feel So Funky
Achievements.Description: Get slimed by a charging ghost.

Achievements.Name: Total Protonic Reversal
Achievements.Description: Knock yourself down with your own weapon.

Achievements.Name: You Gotta Try This Pole!
Achievements.Description: Slide down the fire pole.

Achievements.Name: It's Slime Time
Achievements.Description: Use the Slime Tether on 15 ghosts.

Achievements.Name: I Looked at the Trap, Ray!
Achievements.Description: Recover 20 of your own full ghost traps.

Achievements.Name: Kosher!
Achievements.Description: Remedy a dubious food choice to make the bar mitzvah as orthodox as it can be.

Achievements.Name: I Love You When You Rough-House!
Achievements.Description: The tidy arcitectural office could use some Proton-based humbling.

Achievements.Name: But the Kids Love Us!
Achievements.Description: The children's reading room has a story to tell, but it will take more than your eyes to see it.

Achievements.Name: You Never Studied
Achievements.Description: Keep your ears open to learn everything you can about the Civil War.

Achievements.Name: I've Quit Better Jobs Than This.
Achievements.Description: Some ghosts had a real blowout in the Coat Room.  Clean it up?

Achievements.Name: Hedgebuster
Achievements.Description: The hedge maze is a real eyesore; do some Protonic pruning.

Achievements.Name: One down, on the Ground!
Achievements.Description: Airborne coffins are an affront to gravity; use your Proton Pack to avenge Mother Nature!

Achievements.Name: Ghostbusters Drinking Game
Achievements.Description: Quench your thirst wherever possible to avoid being scared spitless.

Achievements.Name: Loans Paid Off
Achievements.Description: More than $100,000 earned in Xbox LIVE.

Achievements.Name: On the Payroll
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete one Xbox LIVE campaign.

Achievements.Name: Egon's Guinea Pig
Achievements.Description: Use one of every pickup (both power-ups and equipment).

Achievements.Name: Payday!
Achievements.Description: Be the overall top earner in each Xbox LIVE campaign setting.

Achievements.Name: It's a Living
Achievements.Description: Trap over 50 ghosts in your Xbox LIVE Ghostbusting career.

Achievements.Name: Wanted!
Achievements.Description: Defeat three Most Wanted Ghosts.

Achievements.Name: Employee of the Month
Achievements.Description: Be top earner in each Xbox LIVE job type.

Achievements.Name: No Job Too Big
Achievements.Description: Defeat all Most Wanted Ghosts.

Achievements.Name: Gozer's Most Wanted
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete each Xbox LIVE job in every location.

Achievements.Name: Overachiever
Achievements.Description: Get over $2,500,000 in Xbox LIVE, over 30 post-job awards, 50 jobs completed.

Achievements.Name: We Have the Talent!
Achievements.Description: Complete the Firehouse training level.

Achievements.Name: The Flowers are Still Standing!
Achievements.Description: Complete the 'Welcome to the Hotel Sedgewick' level.

Achievements.Name: Once S'more into the Breach
Achievements.Description: Complete the 'Panic in Times Square' level.

Achievements.Name: Get Her!
Achievements.Description: Complete the 'Checking Out the Library' level.

Achievements.Name: Ghost Fever Grips New York
Achievements.Description: Complete the 'Museum of (Super)Natural History' level.

Achievements.Name: Somebody Saw a Cockroach on 12
Achievements.Description: Complete the 'Return to the Sedgewick' level.

Achievements.Name: Let Me Guess, Gozer Worshippers
Achievements.Description: Complete the 'Lost Island Rising' level.

Achievements.Name: Disaster of Biblical Proportions
Achievements.Description: Complete the 'Central Park Cemetery' level.
